snippet.title: Above Earth Trailer (Alpha)
snippet.description:
This is the first official trailer for Above Earth; a survival game set aboard a space station in high Earth orbit after a global calamity.

Now Available On Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1131450/Above_Earth/
